gaffer.data.elementdefinition

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaffer.data.elementdefinition.Type

  • public class Type
extends Object
    A Type contains the an object's java class along with how to validate and aggregate the object. It is used to deserialise/serialise a DataSchema to/from JSON.
